pageProduct.name: SUP Shots Focus 8x50ml Vials
pageProduct.description:
General Information

For a razor sharp mind.

CLEAR, SHARP, FOCUSED
Performing at your best in a fast-paced world requires motivation, high energy and a sharp mind. Unfortunately, coffee and energy drinks just won't get you there. Our experts have developed a 'next generation' SUP to support mental performance and reduce fatigue.

WHY SHOT SUP?
Drink your supplements on-the-go with our super shots. SUP contains a blend of Vitamin B12 & B6, Ginseng and a hint of Caffeine to help: 
  • Mental Performance
  • Support energy metabolism
  • Reduce tiredness and fatigue
SHOTSUP

Size: 8x50mL

KEY FEATURES

• Contains Vitamin Bs
• Contains Caffeine
• Contains Ginseng
• Shot your vitamins on-the-go

Warnings

Contains caffeine [16mg/50mL shot].
Not recommended for children, pregnant or breastfeeding women or people sensitive to caffeine. No more than 50ml should be consumed per day. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Ingredients

Water, Fresh ginseng extract, Apple juice concentrate, Sweeteners (erythritol, steviol glycoside), Flavour (citric acid monohydrate), Stabiliser (HM Pectin), Natural orange flavour, Natural passionfruit flavour, Goji extract, Natural apple flavour, Caffeine, Ginkgo extract, Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12), Pyridoxine hydrochloride (Vitamin B6)

Contains: CONTAINS CAFFEINE

Allergen Contains: Caffeine

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

SHOT 1 SUP (50mL) per day to help boost focus.
Shake before opening. Do not use if tamper evidence seal is broken or missing.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
